- (23, -20): need to find this value

Let me work out the values systematically. At (22,-22) we have 2025.

Moving up from (22,-22): 2026 at (22,-21), 2027 at (22,-20), ... up to (22,22)
That's 45 numbers (2026-2070).

Then left along top: 2071 at (21,22), etc.

For the neighbors:
